author: chirino
msg: - Switched to using camel case in the xml emlement names to make things consistent.
- Replaced the asyncReplication property in the ReplicationService with a minimumReplicas properties.  When set to 0, async replication will be in effect.
- Also removed the use of a map to track replication requests since at most, only 1 sync requrest is issued at a time.

author: eglynn
msg: Fix for handleMessage() being called instead of handleFault() on JAX-WS SOAPHandlers for incoming fault messages. Also fix for incomplete population of SAAJ model in the presence of faults.
